  "title": "Assistant Contract Manager (A2 Construction Company) (Up to $7000 / 5 days / Kaki Bukit)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Assistant Contract Manager (A2 Construction Company) (ID4672)<br />Location: Kaki Bukit<br />Working Hours: Mon to Fri 8.00am-5.00pm<br />Salary: $6000-$7000<br /><br />Responsibilities:<br />• Responsible for a proper contract administration of both the Main Contract and subcontracts including following up of receiving and making payments.<br />• Controlling plan, schedule and cost of the Works<br />• Formulate and maintain the cost control monitoring program for the project<br />• Drafting, reviewing and responding to the contractual correspondence<br />• Identify and prepare Variations and Claims reports<br />• Carry out all sub-contracts awards and purchasing in coordination/correlation with the Design Coordination and Construction Departments<br /><br />Requirement<br />• Degree in Quantity Surveying or its equivalent<br />• Min 2-3 years Assistant Contract Manager on Main-con experience or Builder Company.<br />• Good interpersonal skill<br />• Strong troubleshooting skill and analytical mind<br />• Self-motivated and team player</p>",
